    </subsection>
  
    <subsection xml:id="functions-objectives">
        <title>Objectives</title>
        <ul>
            <li><p>identify formal parameters and parameter values in a code sample</p></li>
            <li><p>predict the return value of a function given sample parameter values</p></li>
            <li><p>define functions with appropriate names for formal parameter</p></li>
            <li><p>apply the accumulator pattern inside of a function</p></li>
            <li><p>explain the purpose of packages and modules in programming </p></li>
            <li><p>utilize existing modules from the Python Standard Library </p></li>
            <li><p>identify whether a function is a modifier and has side effects</p></li>
        </ul>
    </subsection>    


</section>